            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1255.-step-5-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve the <strong>beef stock mix</strong> in 150ml [195ml]  <span class=\"text-danger\">[250ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Add the<strong> beef stock</strong> and the juice of <strong>half</strong> your<strong> lime[s] </strong>to the pan<strong> </strong>and cook for 3-4 min further</p><p>Remove the <strong>smoky</strong> <strong>beans</strong> from the heat and mash into a semi-smooth paste – these are your <strong>smoky</strong> <strong>refried beans</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2155.-step-6.2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2155.-step-6.2-x400.jpg",
