            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2155.-step-6.2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the juice of the <strong>remaining lime</strong> with 1 tbsp [1 1/2 tbsp] <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> in a bowl</p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Add the<strong> shredded lettuce </strong>and<strong> diced tomato </strong>to the bowl and give it a good mix up – this is your <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>salad</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1255.-step-7-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1255.-step-7-x400.jpg",
