            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1255.-step-7-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>To assemble, top the <strong>cooked rice </strong>with the <strong>crispy cumin beef</strong> and serve the<strong> chopped salad </strong>and <strong>refried smoky beans</strong> to the side – this is your <strong>beef & smoky black bean burrito bowl</strong></p><p>Drizzle over the <strong>chipotle yoghurt </strong>and<strong> </strong>sprinkle over the <strong>grated cheese</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
